name: A Story Beings
description:
Welcome, stranger! You are at the very start of a magical visual story. Sit back and enjoy, but also be vigilant. You can unexpectedly become part of our story of color, shades, light, and fire. And playing with fire could be dangerous.

Character from a live performance from Fireter - a theater of shadow and fire. Also a storyteller.

Original NFT from
www.fireter.com
